    <h3>Related Keywords</h3><p><strong>Transform</strong>: When the transform condition is met, you must immediately sac [this] and you can summon from your XD a [Transformed] creature.</p><p><strong>Prone</strong>: Prone creatures cannot move or rotate during their next Move Action (they must instead spend it to get up). They can still be moved or rotated by effects.</p>

